    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The 2019 validation campaign against adult CPB operating conditions is judged sufficient to support the original COU. The assessment team acknowledges that the operating envelope has expanded to include paediatric and neonatal flow rates since initial model release, and that no re-validation evidence covering the low-flow regime (0.3–1.2 L/min) has been generated or linked. This gap is recorded as an observation; the overall credibility package is accepted pending future supplemental validation.",
